CAPE TOWN - The body of a 15-year-old teenager who disappeared in the West Coast community of Vredendal has been found. Ricardo Khasi was last seen by his guardian on Monday. According to a Facebook post by the Vredendal Olifantsrivier Association for Persons With Disabilities, Khasi was autistic. The details surrounding his disappearance are unclear at this stage. A death inquest case has been registered. 